Class ClassArtifact

java.lang.Object
  com.objetdirect.gwt.umlapi.client.artifacts.UMLArtifact
      com.objetdirect.gwt.umlapi.client.artifacts.BoxArtifact
          com.objetdirect.gwt.umlapi.client.artifacts.ClassArtifact

public class ClassArtifact
extends BoxArtifact

This class is an artifact used to represent a class.
A class is divided in three ClassPartArtifact :

  • ClassPartNameArtifact For the name and stereotype part
  • ClassPartAttributesArtifact For the attribute list part
  • ClassPartMethodsArtifact For the method list part

Author:
Florian Mounier (mounier-dot-florian.at.gmail'dot'com)
